# Local development overrides (copy to .dev.vars — it is gitignored).
# TOPOLOGY_URL=demo probes the bundled demo topology (real public endpoints,
# plus one always-DEGRADED and one always-DOWN component) instead of fetching
# topology.yaml from GitHub main.
TOPOLOGY_URL=demo

# --- Optional: test the full GitHub issues integration locally ---
# Point at a personal sandbox repo (NOT wardnet/wardnet-status) and use a
# fine-grained PAT scoped to that repo only, with Issues read/write.
# With these set, the demo's "Legacy Service" opens a real issue after
# ~3 cycles and escalates it to DOWN; edit its URL in src/demo-topology.ts
# to a real site afterwards to watch the issue get closed on recovery.
# GITHUB_REPO=<your-username>/<sandbox-repo>
# GH_ISSUES_TOKEN=github_pat_...

# --- Optional: notification channels ---
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=...
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=...
# NTFY_TOPIC=...
